<center><h1><b>MinSpeak and mobile phones</b></h1></center>
<br><br>
MinSpeak with the proper use of icons and speech synthesizer can be adequately used in mobile phones.
Thought no contract has yet been signed but NOKIA will soon be the first to provide iconic laguages in its mobile phones.
<br>
A new device based On MinSpeak has been designed by Bruce Baker for mobile phones.
The limiting factor in using MinSpeak for mobile phones is its small size. So this set has just 18 icons and ten digits 
to produce a range of vocabulary. Whenever you press an icon voice is generated.
<br><br>
It has following 18 icons:<br><br>
