<br><br>
Now every icon has its specific meaning according to the grammar.<br>
Eg. Left hand for "LAST", Right for "NEXT", Sundial for "TIME" etc.<br><br>
The sequence of icons generate words like in,<br>
For eg. EYE and STOP denotes "SIGN OFF", EYE and FLAGS denote "GREETINGS".<br><br>
Again combination of further icons helps to form phrases or sentences like in,<br>
EYE and STOP and RIGHT HAND denote "BE RIGHT BACK", 
EYE and FLAGS and UP denotes "WHATS UP".
<br><br>

Thus by knowing the meanings of the icons and by learning the grammar a wide range of vocabulary 
can be generated which will aid in easy communication by mobile phones mainly for those who have impaired speech
or language diversities.







